We have a modern stack consisting of Go (golang), AWS ECS, Docker, Javascript, React, GraphQL, Kafka, and others! If any of this sounds interesting, we&#x27;d love to hear from you! Check out our open positions at <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;segment.com&#x2F;engineering#jobs" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;segment.com&#x2F;engineering#jobs</a> If you have specific questions, feel free to reach out to me directly alan ⒜ segment.com (but please do apply on the site).
